alejandro de tomaso (july 10, 1928 in buenos aires â€“ may 21, 2003 in modena, italy) was a racing driver and businessman from argentina. his name is sometimes seen in an italianised form as alessandro de tomaso. he participated in two formula one world championship grands prix, debuting on january 13, 1957. he scored no championship points. he later founded the italian sports car company de tomaso automobili in 1959.